Apple today seeded a surprise release candidate version of <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/macos-sequoia/">macOS Sequoia</a> 15.7, an update that will follow the &zwnj;macOS Sequoia&zwnj; 15.6 update from last week.<br/>
<br/>
